although for instance my little place is out in the country one of its drawbacks is that it doesn't I can't see it unless something happens it forming a sense of community around people who do similar things because everybody who comes to me then sort of disappears back to where they live which is basically all over the place whereas when you have a centre in the city what it does it creates a little focal point and there's a

