other if you don't if you don't have other people you're not being there's a danger of you living in your own little in your own little world and when we live in our own little world we don't see we don't see where we're going wrong yeah you need you need other people in a sense to correct your behavior and to be a to to to to correspond with yeah to sort of resonate with and so

