118
00:13:26,947 --> 00:13:27,928
You don't even think about it.

119
00:13:27,948 --> 00:13:28,470
You're just done.

120
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:37,999
And then while you're drinking your coffee, your mind's running all over the place and you finish your cup of coffee and you think, hold on, did I have that cup of coffee or did I not have that cup of coffee?

121
00:13:38,907 --> 00:13:39,988
Completely lost.

122
00:13:41,730 --> 00:13:42,751
No memory of it at all.

123
00:13:42,772 --> 00:13:45,075
And you think, well, I'll have another one.

124
00:13:45,095 --> 00:13:47,839
